These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, cranberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, car
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | papaya   | cranberry   |
| Transport   | car | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea   |
| Sport      | sailing | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, gospel
1. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | blueberry | avocado |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, asparagus
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | asparagus | pepper |
| Pet    | guinea-pig    | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
